<item>
            <title>[LU-11748] Maloo: tests are reported as failed while they run fine</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11748</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Failed optional test review-dne-zfs-part-4 on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-53vm6: [https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/456887b0-6287-497f-8357-d511966ac54c] ran 10 tests. 7 tests failed: insanity, replay-ost-single, sanity-quota, sanity-dom, sanity-flr, sanity-pfl, replay-single.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maloo reports insanity, replay-ost-single, sanity-quota, sanity-dom, sanity-flr, sanity-pfl as failed because they were unable to remove directory which left after replay-single.sh:test_80f failed with &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11366&quot; title=&quot;replay-single timeout test 80f: rm: cannot remove &amp;#39;/mnt/lustre/d80f.replay-single/remote_dir&amp;#39;: Input/output error&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11366&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11366&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== insanity test complete, duration 2669 sec ========================================================= 05:29:40 (1541654980)
rm: cannot remove &apos;/mnt/lustre/d80f.replay-single&apos;: Directory not empty
 insanity : @@@@@@ FAIL: remove sub-test dirs failed 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
